      <p>I&#8217;d been wondering about this mystical pizza ever since you told me about it. If it&#8217;s really as good as you say it is, I&#8217;m ready to hop on a plane to NY right now! Either that or I may just have to try recreating it myself. NOT that it will be anything like the real thing, of course, but in these pizza underpriveleged parts of the world we have to make do somehow&#8230;</p>
